trans-unit.source: Provides trace event data specific to a thread and a process.
trans-unit.target: Gir hendelsen sporingsdata spesifikke for en tråd og en prosess.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The TraceEventCache class, designed as a performance optimization for trace listener calls, is of interest only to developers creating custom trace listeners.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE]> TraceEventCache klassen, utviklet som et optimalisere ytelsen for spore lytteren samtaler er interessante bare for utviklere å opprette egendefinerte sporingslyttere.

trans-unit.source: The TraceEventCache class is used as a parameter in tracing methods to accurately identify the source of a trace event.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TraceEventCache brukes som en parameter i sporing metoder til å identifisere nøyaktig kilden til en sporingshendelse.

trans-unit.source: Examples of methods that use TraceEventCache are <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceFilter.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Eksempler på metoder som bruker TraceEventCache er <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceFilter.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceFilter.ShouldTrace%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListener.TraceEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache.LogicalOperationStack%2A> property contains data that can be used to correlate the trace with related traces.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache.LogicalOperationStack%2A>egenskapen inneholder data som kan brukes til å sammenligne trace med relaterte sporinger.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache.LogicalOperationStack%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets the call stack for the current thread.
trans-unit.target: Henter kallstakken for gjeldende tråd.

trans-unit.source: The Callstack property gets the call stack from the <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A> property of the <xref:System.Environment> class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Callstack henter kallstakken fra <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>egenskapen for <xref:System.Environment>klassen.</xref:System.Environment> </xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: The property value lists method calls in reverse chronological order.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapsverdien viser metodekall i omvendt kronologisk rekkefølge.

trans-unit.source: That is, the most recent method call is described first.
trans-unit.target: Det vil si beskrives siste metodekallet først.

trans-unit.source: One line of stack trace information is listed for each method call on the stack.
trans-unit.target: En linje i bunken sporingsinformasjon er oppført for hver metodekallet i stakken.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>.</xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string containing stack trace information.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder stakk sporingsinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: This value can be an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Denne verdien kan være en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets the date and time at which the event trace occurred.
trans-unit.target: Henter datoen og klokkeslettet da hendelsen sporingen oppstod.

trans-unit.source: The first time the property is accessed in an instance of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache> class, the current time is returned.
trans-unit.target: Første gang egenskapen brukes i en forekomst av den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache>class, gjeldende klokkeslett returneres.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceEventCache>

trans-unit.source: Subsequent queries of this property in that instance return that same <xref:System.DateTime> value, allowing it to be used as a timestamp.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer det samme etterfølgende spørringer for denne egenskapen i forekomsten <xref:System.DateTime>verdi, og tillater at den brukes som et tidsstempel.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> structure whose value is a date and time expressed in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.DateTime>struktur med en verdi er en dato og klokkeslett som er uttrykt i Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets the correlation data, contained in a stack.
trans-unit.target: Henter Korrelasjons dataene, i en bunke.

trans-unit.source: The correlation data is stored as an object in the call context with the name "System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManagerSlot".
trans-unit.target: Korrelasjonsdata lagres som et objekt i konteksten kall med navnet "System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManagerSlot".

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager> class provides methods used to store a logical operation identity in a thread-bound context and automatically tag each trace event generated by the thread with the stored identity.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>klassen inneholder metoder som brukes til å lagre en logisk operasjon-ID i en kontekst som er bundet til tråd og kode automatisk hver sporingshendelsen som er generert av en tråd med lagrede identiteten.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager> is accessed through the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>er tilgjengelig via den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.CorrelationManager%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager>

trans-unit.source: Each call to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StartLogicalOperation%2A> method pushes a new logical operation identity onto the stack.
trans-unit.target: Hvert kall til den <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StartLogicalOperation%2A>metoden pusher en ny ID for logisk operasjon på stakken.</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StartLogicalOperation%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each call to the <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StopLogicalOperation%2A> method pops a logical operation identity from the stack
trans-unit.target: Hvert kall til <xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StopLogicalOperation%2A>metoden kommer en logisk operasjon ID fra stakken</xref:System.Diagnostics.CorrelationManager.StopLogicalOperation%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Stack"></xref> containing correlation data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Stack"> </xref> som inneholder korrelasjonsdata.

trans-unit.source: Gets the unique identifier of the current process.
trans-unit.target: Henter den unike identifikatoren for den gjeldende prosessen.

trans-unit.source: Until the process terminates, the process identifier uniquely identifies the process throughout the system.
trans-unit.target: Før du avslutter prosessen identifiserer prosess-IDen prosessen i hele systemet.

trans-unit.source: The system-generated unique identifier of the current process.
trans-unit.target: Systemgenererte unike identifikatoren for den gjeldende prosessen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a unique identifier for the current managed thread.
trans-unit.target: Henter en unik ID for gjeldende forvaltet tråd.

trans-unit.source: The thread identifier is the value of the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.ManagedThreadId%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property formatted as a string.
trans-unit.target: Tråd-IDen er verdien for den <xref:System.Threading.Thread.ManagedThreadId%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen formatert som en streng.</xref:System.Threading.Thread.ManagedThreadId%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A string that represents a unique integer identifier for this managed thread.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer en unik heltall identifikator for denne administrerte tråden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the current number of ticks in the timer mechanism.
trans-unit.target: Henter gjeldende antall merker i tidtakeren mekanisme.

trans-unit.source: The get accessor calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to get the timestamp.
trans-unit.target: Hent aksessor kall av <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode for å hente tidsstempelet.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch> class uses a high-resolution performance counter, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A> returns the current value of that counter.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch>klassen bruker en med høy oppløsning ytelsesteller <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A>returnerer gjeldende verdi for denne telleren.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch> class uses the system timer, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A> returns the <xref:System.DateTime.Ticks%2A> property of <xref:System.DateTime.Now%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch>klassen bruker tidtaker, <xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A>returnerer <xref:System.DateTime.Ticks%2A>for <xref:System.DateTime.Now%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.DateTime.Now%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.DateTime.Ticks%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch.GetTimestamp%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Stopwatch>

trans-unit.source: The tick counter value of the underlying timer mechanism.
trans-unit.target: Aksemerker tellerverdien for den underliggende mekanismen tidtaker.
